<div class="text-24 text parbase section">

<p>Slate may change or terminate these Terms for any reason at any time.&nbsp; Slate reserves the right, in its sole discretion, to restrict, suspend, or terminate your access to and use of the Services, with or without prior notice.&nbsp; Otherwise applicable sections of the Terms shall survive termination.&nbsp; Slate also reserves the right to seek all remedies available at law and in equity for violations of these Terms. &nbsp;Upon termination, you must cease all use of the Services, including any of the Slate Content.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>


